	year={2002},
	annotate={
		This paper approaches a chess program in a different way. Instead of
		using the very commong alpha-beta algorithm, it attempts to employ an
		evolving method. While I do not intent to create an evolving algorithm,
		this paper still had potential as it also discusses some of the more
